title: Top 10 Kickers and Top 10 Punters in the NFL entering the 2020 season (Football 7/4)
description:
It's the podcast you've been waiting for! What better way to celebrate a holiday than listening to John Breech break down kickers and punters. That's what he does on this episode with host Will Brinson. The guys discuss Breech's top 10 list for each position. Will Josh Lambo get the credit he deserves? Can you name a punter that's not on your favorite team? Strap in for the special teams analysis you never knew you needed.
'Pick Six' is available on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, Stitcher, Google Podcasts, Castbox, Bullhorn and wherever else you listen to podcasts.
